        <div class="section-heading" id="prayer-request">
            <span class="section-heading-icon" aria-hidden="true">✉️</span>
            <h2>Prayer Request</h2>
            <span class="section-heading-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>

        <p>If you would like us to pray for you, please fill in the form below with
        as much or as little information as you wish. All requests are treated with
        complete confidentiality.</p>
        <p>If you would like us to pray <em>with</em> you, please provide a phone
        number or email address and we will be in touch.</p>

        <form class="prayer-form" id="prayerForm">

            <p class="form-note">Fields marked <span class="required">*</span> are required.</p>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="prayerName">Name <span class="required">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="prayerName" name="name" required
                    placeholder="Your name" />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="prayerEmail">Email</label>
                <input type="email" id="prayerEmail" name="email"
                    placeholder="Your email address" />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="prayerPhone">Phone</label>
                <input type="tel" id="prayerPhone" name="phone"
                    placeholder="Your phone number" />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="prayerMessage">Prayer Request <span class="required">*</span></label>
                <textarea id="prayerMessage" name="prayerRequest" required
                    placeholder="Please share your prayer request here..." rows="6"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group form-check">
                <input type="checkbox" id="prayerPrivate" name="isPrivate" />
                <label for="prayerPrivate">Keep this request private (prayer team only)</label>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group form-check">
                <input type="checkbox" id="prayerZoom" name="wantZoom" />
                <label for="prayerZoom">Please send me details of how to join the
                    Monday prayer meeting on Zoom</label>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Send Prayer Request</button>
            <div id="prayerStatus"></div>

        </form>

        <p class="form-note">Your request will be handled with care and confidentiality by our prayer team.</p>

